{"tid":2493547,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"經過巨人結局後我決定唔再追新動漫","createTime":"2021-04-18T04:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T05:02:25.000Z","uid":64005,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"66bd29a8f75849ab9da6f72e51556ab4fcb8098e","tid":2493547,"uid":64005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:01:17.000Z","msg":"近十年我追既東京喰種又係咁<br />\n巨人又係咁<br />\n鬼滅還好因為我落坑果陣都差唔多結局唔洗追咁耐<br />\n<br />\n本身覺得係神作既動漫<br />\n俾我有無限既幻想空間<br />\n對結局充滿期待<br />\n經常想快啲出下一集<br />\n停刊停播我會失落<br />\n連載期間仲會不斷重溫唔同集數<br />\n點知追左十年八年到最後原來係篤屎黎<br />\n巨人直程睇完最後一話之後我無再想重溫任何集數<br />\n無再諗呢套野既劇情既慾望<br />\n睇到最後令我覺得呢個故事好似低俗笑話咁<br />\n<br />\n我依家唔會再追新動漫<br />\n除非出哂我先會再睇<br />\n要我再一次追幾年點知爛尾既動漫真係慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8565e8e1383b1afa878988e5f121a020c194b7","tid":2493547,"uid":110878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:02:19.000Z","msg":"岩 睇天使得得b算啦"},{"pid":"a9732130563cdc27cce318348c7f30a29c5a0ea1","tid":2493547,"uid":200529,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:03:37.000Z","msg":"好喔&nbsp;酷欸"},{"pid":"2545d42e50caed1bafee9073e19ccb45994e2352","tid":2493547,"uid":189417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:12:13.000Z","msg":"讚"},{"pid":"19eab9e7faade1ba84226163078617fe0acbdab1","tid":2493547,"uid":370062,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:13:14.000Z","msg":"追手機俠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n包你滿意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXuQcz1rZ3UcFUpSdLVQESL1BqHpDvFZfhLDttZxRVfU5?filename=QtZVJJg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQtZVJJg.png&h=b6279267&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d4f518f073e9540f0a35042e610c84454052c5a","tid":2493547,"uid":361609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:24:22.000Z","